590
00:31:42,110 --> 00:31:42,720
Mr. Xie,

591
00:31:43,160 --> 00:31:43,830
what is the meaning of this?

592
00:31:44,270 --> 00:31:46,160
The day I entered the Immortals Array to repair the barrier,

593
00:31:46,440 --> 00:31:47,920
