780
00:40:17,550 --> 00:40:19,760
Boundless Mountain!

781
00:40:25,070 --> 00:40:27,920
That's Fajian's ultimate move, Boundless Mountain.

782
00:40:28,550 --> 00:40:29,670
Once unleashed,

783
00:40:30,230 --> 00:40:31,480
